'''約瑟夫·查爾斯·施瑞納'''（{{lang-en|Joseph Charles Schriner}}；{{bd|1955年|3月3日}}），是一名美國[[行动主义|政治活動家]]和記者，2020年到2016年間曾五度競逐[[美國總統|美國總統]]職務<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.starbeacon.com/archives/in-the-presidential-campaign-it-was-joe-the-plumber-in/article_83ec78a2-367c-54b6-852b-4c1e6bd8d3c2.html|title = In the 2008 presidential campaign it was Joe the Plumber. In 2012 it's going to be Joe the Painter.|date = January 14, 2009|accessdate = September 15, 2015|publisher = Star Beacon}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.voteforjoe.com/#!declaration-speech/c45p|title = Schriner 2016 declaration speech podcast|date = September 12, 2015|accessdate = September 15, 2015|website = www.voteforjoe.com|archive-date = 2000-04-16|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20000416175018/http://www.voteforjoe.com/#!declaration-speech/c45p|dead-url = no}}</ref>。他倡導[[基督教民主主義|基督教民主主義]]，主要是作為獨立候選人競選，直至[[2020年美國總統選舉|2020年美國總統選舉]]改以[[美國團結黨|美國團結黨]]身分參選<ref>{{cite web |last1=Shome |first1=Amol |title=(Some) 2020 Presidential Candidates |url=http://cchscentaurian.com/2019/04/09/some-2020-presidential-candidates/ |website=The Centaurian |date=April 9, 2019}}</ref><ref name="Running as American Solidarity candidate1">{{cite web |last1=Schriner |first1=Joe |title=Declaration Speech 2020 |url=https://www.voteforjoe.com/declaration-speech |website=Average Joe "The Painter" Schriner for President 2020 |accessdate=9 February 2019 |archive-date=2020-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126234305/https://www.voteforjoe.com/declaration-speech |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Running as American Solidarity candidate2">{{cite web |last1=Schriner |first1=Joe |title=Joe Schriner's Presidential Declaration! 2020 Vision! |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IFoIq0vZPIo |website=YouTube |accessdate=9 February 2019 |archive-date=2019-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190427071912/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IFoIq0vZPIo |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他曾在2000年和2016年大選週期初期以[[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]]人身份參選<ref>{{cite news|url = http://www.csmonitor.com/2000/0208/p3s1.html|title = A van, a message, and a mission|date = February 8, 2000|accessdate = September 15, 2015|newspaper = Christian Science Monitor|archive-date = 2020-10-07|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201007172741/https://www.csmonitor.com/2000/0208/p3s1.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>，也曾在2008年大選週期競逐[[美国绿党|绿党]]總統候選人資格但失敗<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yWCxuUp8pw4|title = Green Party Presidential Candidate Forum talk, Reading, PA.|date = July 2007|accessdate = October 14, 2016|archive-date = 2019-08-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190805035253/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yWCxuUp8pw4|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

在成為[[常年候選人|常年候選人]]之前，施瑞納花費大量的時間在美國各地旅行，並即席對他遇到的個人進行專訪。他聲稱，與經驗豐富的決策者相比，這些主觀經歷使他對國家的社會、政治和經濟問題有了更深入的了解。這些年來，他已經接受了眾多媒體採訪，並曾在多家大學發表演講<ref name="College Talks">{{Cite web|url = http://www.voteforjoe.com/college-talks|title = College Talks|accessdate = October 14, 2016|website = www.voteforjoe.com|archive-date = 2020-11-27|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201127004643/https://www.voteforjoe.com/college-talks|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

在媒體裡，施瑞林被稱為「普通人」（{{lang|en|average Joe}}）<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.nptelegraph.com/average-joe-runs-for-president/article_d217148f-d741-5f12-8363-e967d20b698b.html|title = "Average Joe" Runs for President |date = May 25, 2004|accessdate = September 12, 2015|publisher = The North Platte Telegraph}}</ref>，有時也被稱為「油漆工喬」（{{lang|en|Joe the Painter}}）<ref>{{cite news |last1=Feather |first1=Carl |title=In the 2008 presidential campaign, it was Joe the Plumber. In 2012, it's going to be Joe the Painter |url=https://www.starbeacon.com/archives/in-the-2008-presidential-campaign-it-was-joe-the-plumber-in-2012-it-s-going/article_83ec78a2-367c-54b6-852b-4c1e6bd8d3c2.html |accessdate=18 August 2020 |work=Star Beacon |date=14 January 2009 |language=en}}</ref>。目前他是個體經營的[[裝修|房屋油漆工]]<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.voteforjoe.com/#!making-a-living/c17zs|title = Making a Living|date = September 12, 2015|accessdate = September 12, 2015|website = www.voteforjoe.com|archive-date = 2000-04-16|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20000416175018/http://www.voteforjoe.com/#!making-a-living/c17zs|dead-url = no}}</ref>，亦是其家鄉報紙《布拉夫頓新聞》（{{lang|en|The Bluffton News}}）的自由撰稿人<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.blufftonnews.com/node?page=1|title = Bluffton News (pen name: "Average Joe") multiple stories|date = September 17, 2005|accessdate = September 12, 2015|archive-date = 2016-10-21|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161021153925/http://blufftonnews.com/node?page=1|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

